{"tid":908051,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[正義得勝］退休攝影師覆核勝訴　政府關閉「公民廣場」被裁違憲","createTime":"2018-11-19T09:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T07:12:06.000Z","uid":389,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb1a3e311ba9757c25b2a095bd9ce3034f55b60","tid":908051,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZBV6UVz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBV6UVz.png&h=70b20f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府2014年、即前特首梁振英任內，決定關閉被稱為「公民廣場」的政總東翼前地，更在四周築起圍欄，訂下守則，禁止市民在周一至周六進入，周日舉行集會則要申請，退休攝影師張德榮不滿政府限制市民的集會和表達自由，同年入稟司法覆核。高院法官區慶祥今日頒下裁決，裁定政府做法違憲。<br />\n<br />\n區慶祥今日判辭中指出，政府關閉公民廣場的做法，違反基本法27條，人權法案16條及17條。<br />\n<br />\n申請人一方指出，政府全面禁止所有人在周一至周六，進入公民廣場行使表達自由及集會權利，而周日及公眾假期需要申請，有關限制明顯不相稱（disproportionate），行政署長指有關限制可確保政府總部正常運作，法官在判訊中認同申請所指出，政府的限制已經超過，讓政總有效運作的目的所需，而行政署長未有解釋周一至周六全面禁止的理據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E5%8B%9D%E8%A8%B4-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89-%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4-%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%258B%259D%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2586%25B2%2F&d=LXTajXi0ZXdg8PiXCkbgC%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=602f0e3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%258B%259D%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2586%25B2%2F&h=4a621624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E5%8B%9D%E8%A8%B4-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89-%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4-%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"7b282dba99c80244763f6381dacc78acd6ec0deb","tid":908051,"uid":29880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:03:44.000Z","msg":"呢個法官好似判過好多義士敗訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28b4e919285e16f6af66d34e84a1aa811032dc7","tid":908051,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2cbafbf7ff585cdb7ff577184753d05f018a8e","tid":908051,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7b282dba99c80244763f6381dacc78acd6ec0deb","tid":908051,"uid":29880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:03:44.000Z","msg":"呢個法官好似判過好多義士敗訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"可能因為封公廣先有雨革"},{"pid":"1fc429c9f5e2ce0542e485ef819afc9c79186abc","tid":908051,"uid":13032,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3e2cbafbf7ff585cdb7ff577184753d05f018a8e","tid":908051,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7b282dba99c80244763f6381dacc78acd6ec0deb","tid":908051,"uid":29880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:03:44.000Z","msg":"呢個法官好似判過好多義士敗訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"可能因為封公廣先有雨革"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T01:56:47.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫公廣<br />\n打公民廣場係咪咁撚辛苦你啫？"},{"pid":"a36d32d7410bb4b7f003fa0a35c5b13210fff28c","tid":908051,"uid":26354,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1fc429c9f5e2ce0542e485ef819afc9c79186abc","tid":908051,"ui